This project is the code for the first Barcelona Yahoo Hack U 24h programming competition, held on February @FIB - UPC.
This project is a Twitter hash controlled Lego Mindstorms, and a webpage for geolocating people who are controlling the robot over the world. The robot also publishes posts to Wordpress, which are also shown in the main website.

Technologies used:

Twitter Stream API
YQL -> Flickr
    -> Google Translate
    -> Wordpress
    -> Yahoo Weather
Google Maps

